{"tid":2264234,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"去年平安夜防暴衝入桔梗 少年從餐廳墮樓受傷 事隔逾10個月被起訴管有雷射筆","createTime":"2020-10-30T13:08:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-30T15:54:51.000Z","uid":240362,"like":10,"dislike":40,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"803df28372400506b681d913b7743851d7b43e51","tid":2264234,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T13:08:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/10834\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F10834&d=e7N1rpd9%2BHLCKfTw7%2FjGdi%2B7EDXmwg1SXj7S5MqlT1o%3D&h=d02e8997\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/10834</a><br />\n<br />\n#九龍城裁判法院第一庭<br />\n#鄭念慈裁判官<br />\n#1225旺角 #新案件 <br />\n<br />\n宋 (16)<br />\n<br />\n控罪：在公眾地方管有攻擊性武器<br />\n被控於2019年12月25日，在旺角彌敦道678號外的公眾地方無合法權限或合理辯解而攜有攻擊性武器，即1個能發射雷射光束的裝置。<br />\n<br />\n背景：<br />\n去年12月24日平安夜，市民傍晚開始到多區商場報佳音並表達訴求，包括旺角朗豪坊。入夜後多區街頭爆發警民衝突，在旺角，警方發射催淚彈，出動水炮車驅散人群。衝突一直燃燒至聖誕日的凌晨。凌晨約2時半，一名16歲青年，在旺角桔梗餐廳天台因躲避警員追捕而墮樓，入院後曾呼叫：「我不想被消失」。<br />\n（參考 端傳媒報道 (<a href=\"https://theinitium.com/article/20191224-whatsnew-christmas-eve-hk-clash-police/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftheinitium.com%2Farticle%2F20191224-whatsnew-christmas-eve-hk-clash-police%2F&d=e7N1rpd9%2BHLCKfTw7%2FjGdi%2B7EDXmwg1SXj7S5MqlT1o%3D&h=e37f6f21\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://theinitium.com/article/20191224-whatsnew-christmas-eve-hk-clash-police/</a>)）<br />\n<br />\n案件押後至2020年12月11日0930在九龍城裁判法院第一庭再訊<br />\n✅期間獲准保釋，條件包括現金、不得離港、報到及宵禁令等"},{"pid":"946dde3557d78fc31609140e2de00215d7db1b3d","tid":2264234,"uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T13:09:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c81c2c1a55ebf1afa37bdba6d8